  "instructions": [
    "Toast sesame seeds in a dry pan until golden brown, then grind them into powder.",
    "Sauté garlic and onion until translucent, add pepper and cook for another minute.",
    "Add mixed grains to the pan with vegetable oil. Stir-fry until they start to crisp up.",
    "Pour tomato sauce over the grains. Add dried oregano and salt, stir well.",
    "Cook for an additional 5 minutes until all ingredients are heated through.",
    "Garnish with the toasted sesame powder if desired."
